name: ✴ 𝕿𝖎𝖙𝖆𝖓 ✴
description:
✴ Portrait of Titan

The fickle God of your world. One-touch and you sail. Another touch and you sink. It is your everything. One day, the excessive attachment that you have reminds you that you need to go far, far away. 

✴[MAD GOD]✴ is an original dark fantasy series consist of blood and beautiful creatures portraying their life, their pride, and their attitude.
